		<p id="description">Yes it's true, I can show you the world, shining, shimmering, splendid. Click the button just below the earth to load a list of all the worlds countries, regions, and populations. You can then interact with the search field to narrow down the results by country, or population. If searching by population, note that when typing a number, if you add a less-than symbol '<' before the number, you will get a list of all countries that have populations less than or equal to that number. If you add a greater than symbol '>' before the number, well, you get the idea. Once you have narrowed down your search to one result, you will be presented with all of the available data for that country. There's no one to tell us no, or where to go, enjoy the ride.</p>

